1 1 false indirect: TEST_INDIRECT_CLOBBER test_indirect_clobber_target

\ This tests the clobber contract of the generated indirect trampoline.
\ Padding locals put `saved` in x4; the indirect target will clobber x4.
\ The caller must relocate `saved` before calling the trampoline.
fun: test_indirect_clobber_caller { _a _b _c _d saved arg -- out }
  arg test_indirect_clobber_target { called }
  saved called +
end

fun: test_indirect_clobber_target { arg -- out } [ redefine ]
  \ Simulate an unknown target implementation clobbering a non-ABI arg reg.
  [ 444 4 comp_load ]
  arg
end

TEST_INDIRECT_CLOBBER indirect_to' test_indirect_clobber_target

